    "defaultContent": "\n    \u003Cdiv class=\u0022w-full bg-grafana-dark min-h-screen\u0022\u003E\n        \n        \u003C!-- Hero Section --\u003E\n        \u003Cdiv class=\u0022relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-900 to-grafana-dark pt-16 pb-24\u0022\u003E\n            \u003Cdiv class=\u0022container mx-auto px-4 text-center\u0022\u003E\n                \u003Cdiv class=\u0022inline-block mb-4 px-3 py-1 border border-grafana-orange/30 rounded-full bg-grafana-orange/10 text-grafana-orange text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase\u0022\u003E\n                    Observability Platform\n                \u003C/div\u003E\n                \u003Ch1 class=\u0022text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight mb-6\u0022\u003E\n                    Unify Your Data. \u003Cbr\u003E\n                    \u003Cspan class=\u0022text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 to-yellow-500\u0022\u003EAmplify Your Insights.\u003C/span\u003E\n                \u003C/h1\u003E\n                \u003Cp class=\u0022mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-xl text-gray-400\u0022\u003E\n                    The world\u2019s leading open-source platform for observability. Visualize metrics, logs, and traces from any source in a single pane of glass.\n                \u003C/p\u003E\n                \u003Cdiv class=\u0022mt-10 flex justify-center gap-4\u0022\u003E\n                    \u003Cbutton class=\u0022px-8 py-3 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-orange-600 text-white font-bold hover:from-orange-600 hover:to-orange-700 transition shadow-lg shadow-orange-500/20\u0022\u003E\n                        Get Started Free\n                    \u003C/button\u003E\n                    \u003Cbutton class=\u0022px-8 py-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-600 text-white hover:bg-gray-800 transition\u0022\u003E\n                        View Demo\n                    \u003C/button\u003E\n                \u003C/div\u003E\n            \u003C/div\u003E\n        \u003C/div\u003E\n\n        \u003C!-- The Challenge Section --\u003E\n        \u003Cdiv class=\u0022py-16 bg-grafana-panel border-y border-gray-800\u0022\u003E\n            \u003Cdiv class=\u0022container mx-auto px-4\u0022\u003E\n                \u003Cdiv class=\u0022flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12\u0022\u003E\n                    \u003Cdiv class=\u0022md:w-1/2\u0022\u003E\n                        \u003Ch2 class=\u0022text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6\u0022\u003EThe Challenge: \u003Cspan class=\u0022text-red-400\u0022\u003EData Silos\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/h2\u003E\n                        \u003Cp class=\u0022text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed\u0022\u003E\n                            Modern enterprises rely on a complex web of infrastructure. Monitoring this stack typically requires jumping between half a dozen tools: cloud metrics, database logs, and cluster stats.\n                        \u003C/p\u003E\n                        \u003Cp class=\u0022text-lg leading-relaxed\u0022\u003E\n                            \u003Cstrong class=\u0022text-white\u0022\u003EThe Result:\u003C/strong\u003E Context switching kills productivity, increases downtime, and creates \u0022blind spots\u0022 in your architecture.\n                        \u003C/p\u003E\n                    \u003C/div\u003E\n                    \u003Cdiv class=\u0022md:w-1/2 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\u0022\u003E\n                        \u003Cdiv class=\u0022bg-grafana-dark p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-700 text-center opacity-50\u0022\u003E\n                            \u003Ci class=\u0022fas fa-cloud text-3xl mb-2 text-gray-500\u0022\u003E\u003C/i\u003E\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\u0022text-sm\u0022\u003ECloud Metrics\u003C/div\u003E\n                        \u003C/div\u003E\n                        \u003Cdiv class=\u0022bg-grafana-dark p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-700 text-center opacity-50\u0022\u003E\n                            \u003Ci class=\u0022fas fa-database text-3xl mb-2 text-gray-500\u0022\u003E\u003C/i\u003E\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\u0022text-sm\u0022\u003EDB Logs\u003C/div\u003E\n                        \u003C/div\u003E\n                        \u003Cdiv class=\u0022bg-grafana-dark p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-700 text-center opacity-50\u0022\u003E\n                            \u003Ci class=\u0022fas fa-server text-3xl mb-2 text-gray-500\u0022\u003E\u003C/i\u003E\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\u0022text-sm\u0022\u003EK8s Clusters\u003C/div\u003E\n                        \u003C/div\u003E\n                        \u003Cdiv class=\u0022bg-grafana-dark p-6 rounded-xl border border-red-500/50 text-center relative\u0022\u003E\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\u0022absolute -top-3 -right-3 bg-red-500 text-white text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full\u0022\u003EAlert\u003C/div\u003E\n                            \u003Ci class=\u0022fas fa-exclamation-triangle text-3xl mb-2 text-red-500\u0022\u003E\u003C/i\u003E\n                            \u003Cdiv class=\u0022text-sm text-white\u0022\u003EBlind Spot\u003C/div\u003E\n                        \u003C/div\u003E\n                    \u003C/div\u003E\n                \u003C/div\u003E\n            \u003C/div\u003E\n        \u003C/div\u003E\n\n        \u003C!-- Core Features Grid --\u003E\n        \u003Cdiv class=\u0022py-20 container mx-auto px-4\u0022\u003E\n            \u003Cdiv class=\u0022text-center mb-16\u0022\u003E\n                \u003Ch2 class=\u0022text-3xl font-bold text-white\u0022\u003EOperational Intelligence\u003C/h2\u003E\n                \u003Cp class=\u0022text-gray-400 mt-2\u0022\u003EOne platform for all your data.\u003C/p\u003E\n            \u003C/div\u003E\n\n            \u003Cdiv class=\u0022grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\u0022\u003E\n                \u003C!-- Feature 1 --\u003E\n                \u003Cdiv class=\u0022bg-grafana-panel p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-800 hover:border-grafana-orange/50 transition duration-300 group\u0022\u003E\n                    \u003Cdiv class=\u0022w-12 h-12 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-blue-500/20 transition\u0022\u003E\n                        \u003Ci class=\u0022fas fa-layer-group text-blue-400 text-xl\u0022\u003E\u003C/i\u003E\n                    \u003C/div\u003E\n                    \u003Ch3 class=\u0022text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3\u0022\u003EUnified Observability\u003C/h3\u003E\n                    \u003Cp class=\u0022text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\u0022\u003E\n                        Stop moving data. Connect directly to Prometheus, Loki, Elasticsearch, InfluxDB, and 100\u002B other plugins. Visualize everything side-by-side.\n                    \u003C/p\u003E\n                \u003C/div\u003E\n\n                \u003C!-- Feature 2 --\u003E\n                \u003Cdiv class=\u0022bg-grafana-panel p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-800 hover:border-grafana-orange/50 transition duration-300 group\u0022\u003E\n                    \u003Cdiv class=\u0022w-12 h-12 bg-purple-500/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-purple-500/20 transition\u0022\u003E\n                        \u003Ci class=\u0022fas fa-chart-line text-purple-400 text-xl\u0022\u003E\u003C/i\u003E\n                    \u003C/div\u003E\n                    \u003Ch3 class=\u0022text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3\u0022\u003EDynamic Visualization\u003C/h3\u003E\n                    \u003Cp class=\u0022text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\u0022\u003E\n                        From heatmaps to geospatial maps. Use ad-hoc queries to find root causes and annotate graphs to correlate deployments with performance.\n                    \u003C/p\u003E\n                \u003C/div\u003E\n\n                \u003C!-- Feature 3 --\u003E\n                \u003Cdiv class=\u0022bg-grafana-panel p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-800 hover:border-grafana-orange/50 transition duration-300 group\u0022\u003E\n                    \u003Cdiv class=\u0022w-12 h-12 bg-green-500/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-green-500/20 transition\u0022\u003E\n                        \u003Ci class=\u0022fas fa-bell text-green-400 text-xl\u0022\u003E\u003C/i\u003E\n                    \u003C/div\u003E\n                    \u003Ch3 class=\u0022text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3\u0022\u003EUnified Alerting\u003C/h3\u003E\n                    \u003Cp class=\u0022text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\u0022\u003E\n                        Centralize your strategy. Define thresholds visually and send multi-channel notifications to Slack, PagerDuty, and Teams.\n                    \u003C/p\u003E\n                \u003C/div\u003E\n            \u003C/div\u003E\n        \u003C/div\u003E\n\n        \u003C!-- Enterprise Section --\u003E\n        \u003Cdiv class=\u0022py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-black relative\u0022\u003E\n            \u003Cdiv class=\u0022container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10\u0022\u003E\n                \u003Cdiv class=\u0022bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 border border-white/10\u0022\u003E\n                    \u003Cdiv class=\u0022flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-8\u0022\u003E\n                        \u003Cdiv\u003E\n                            \u003Ch2 class=\u0022text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4\u0022\u003EGrafana Enterprise \u0026 Cloud\u003C/h2\u003E\n                            \u003Cp class=\u0022text-gray-400 mb-6 max-w-xl\u0022\u003E\n                                Built for scale. Get high-availability guarantees, long-term retention, and enterprise-grade security.\n                            \u003C/p\u003E\n                            \u003Cul class=\u0022space-y-3\u0022\u003E\n                                \u003Cli class=\u0022flex items-center text-sm text-gray-300\u0022\u003E\n                                    \u003Ci class=\u0022fas fa-check text-grafana-orange mr-3\u00