       Monitor system uptime across distributed Kubernetes clusters. Reduce MTTR by correlating logs and traces.\n                    \u003C/p\u003E\n                \u003C/div\u003E\n                \u003C!-- Case 2 --\u003E\n                \u003Cdiv class=\u0022border border-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-800/50 transition\u0022\u003E\n                    \u003Ch4 class=\u0022text-grafana-orange font-bold mb-2 uppercase text-xs tracking-wider\u0022\u003EIndustrial IoT\u003C/h4\u003E\n                    \u003Cp class=\u0022text-gray-300 text-sm\u0022\u003E\n                        Visualize sensor data from factory floors. Track temperature and vibration to predict equipment failure.\n                    \u003C/p\u003E\n                \u003C/div\u003E\n                \u003C!-- Case 3 --\u003E\n                \u003Cdiv class=\u0022border border-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-800/50 transition\u0022\u003E\n                    \u003Ch4 class=\u0022text-grafana-orange font-bold mb-2 uppercase text-xs tracking-wider\u0022\u003EBusiness Intelligence\u003C/h4\u003E\n                    \u003Cp class=\u0022text-gray-300 text-sm\u0022\u003E\n                        Track active users, sales velocity, and regional performance by connecting directly to SQL and CRMs.\n                    \u003C/p\u003E\n                \u003C/div\u003E\n            \u003C/div\u003E\n        \u003C/div\u003E\n\n        \u003C!-- Footer CTA --\u003E\n        \u003Cdiv class=\u0022border-t border-gray-800 bg-grafana-panel py-12 text-center\u0022\u003E\n            \u003Ch2 class=\u0022text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4\u0022\u003EStop guessing. Start knowing.\u003C/h2\u003E\n            \u003Cp class=\u0022text-gray-400 mb-8\u0022\u003EJoin thousands of companies using Grafana today.\u003C/p\u003E\n            \u003Cbutton class=\u0022px-8 py-3 rounded-lg bg-grafana-orange text-white font-bold hover:bg-orange-600 transition\u0022\u003E\n                Create Free Account\n    